$$
b
b+a
b+2a
$$

$$
(b+2a)^2 - (b+a)^2 - b^2
=
b^2 + 4ab + 4a^2 - b^2 - 2ab - a^2 - b^2
=
3a^2 + 2ab - b^2
=
(3*a-b)*(a+b)
$$

If we choose a value of $b$, want
$$
(3*a-b) * (a+b) < T
$$
$$
3a^2 + 2ab - b < T
$$

If
$$
3a-b = f
a +b  = n/f
$$
$$
[1/4, 1/4]   [f  ]   [a]
[-1/4,3/4] * [n/f] = [b]
$$

$$
[1/4, 1/4]   [1]    [7]
[-1/4,3/4] * [27] = [20]
$$

$$
[1/4, 1/4]   [3]    [3]
[-1/4,3/4] * [9] =  [6]
$$

Given $d1$ want
$$
3d2 - d1 >= 1
d2 >= (d1+1)/3
$$

